title: Pahelika Secret Legends - New HOG Puzzle like Azada - Wendy99
description:
Pahelika Secret Legends - 139 MB

The Legends were true.


There is an ancient secret so powerful, it was buried deep beneath a maze of puzzles and pitfalls 
to prevent anyone from ever laying a hand on it.
Then one man discovered the existence of the secret. In doing so, his life changed forever. He 
resolved to seek the secret. He wanted to know if the legends were true.
They were. 


Pahelika: Secret Legends is a adventure/puzzle game set in a fantasy universe.
The game takes the player on a quest to discover the truth hidden behind an
ancient legend told for generations in his family...


System Requirements: Windows Me/2000/Xp/Vista, Directx 7, 64Mb RAM, Graphics Card.
